two forums for candidates running in the Nov. 8 local election. 
</P>
<P>
 The forum for the candidates for mayor and the council will be held Oct. 5 in 
Room B of the Community Meeting Center at 11300 Stanford Ave. The five mayoral 
candidates will face off from 6 to 7:30 p.m. Then from 8 to 9:30 p.m., the 12 
council candidates will be presented. 
</P>
