<TEXT>
<P>
 Dan Kuiper, the coach of San Diego Francis Parker, took a page out of his old 
eight-man football playbook to beat Southern California Christian, 19-14, 
Friday afternoon. 
</P>
<P>
 With 7 minutes 11 seconds left in the game and his team at the Flames' 36-yard 
line, Kuiper called for a hook-and-ladder play. 
</P>
<P>
