 The Flames (1-2) rallied from a 13-0 deficit late in the second quarter. Ron 
Wood scored on a one-yard run with 11 seconds left in the first half. The 
Flames scored on their first possession of the second half when Ken Buhler's 
27-yard touchdown run at 9:12 capped a six-play, 66-yard drive. BEN STURTEVANT 
