<TEXT>
<P>
 The father of an American youth arrested last year for vandalism and mischief 
was fined Friday for using abusive language against a policeman, a university 
lecturer and a condominium resident. Prosecutors decided not to proceed on two 
charges of assault. 
</P>
<P>
