 NOTABLE QUOTE 
</P>
<P>
 "Kathleen Brown says she opposes the death penalty, but says she'd enforce the 
law. The last person to say that was Rose Bird, and she voted to overturn 68 
death sentences in a row after Jerry Brown appointed her chief justice." 
</P>
<P>
 -- George Gorton, Gov. Pete Wilson's campaign manager, in a statement 
announcing a new ad.BROWN, KATHLEEN 
