<P>
 Monroe 34, Cleveland 29 -- Running back Nick Nutcitelli scored three 
touchdowns and rushed for 212 yards to lead Monroe (1-2) at home.Nutcitelli 
scored on runs of 20, 58 and 38 yards. 
</P>
